# Competitor APK Dumps (Exceeds Windows Path Limits)
reference locker app decompiled/

# Security audit — confidential, never commit
vulnerability.md

# RSA key pair — never commit private key
backend/src/keys/*.pem
backend/keys/*.pem
backend/scripts/src/keys/*.pem
*.pem

# Local signing backups
user-app/keystore_backup/
**/keystore_backup/
